Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Want to commit double suicide with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding... I just thought I'd say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to forget?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, do you feel sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking because you don't look okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go visit Kao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been able to go together lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did he have a fight with Kao-chan, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You okay with that? Saying such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like rubbing salt into your enemy's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he's having issues over music,\Nthen I don't know how to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just think that Kousei will\Ncheer up if he sees Kao-chan, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think it'll\Nkill you to dial it up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For whose sake are you\N studying against your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For whose sake did you choose\Na higher-ranked high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing a high school near\NOkutsu Music College Affiliated High...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! W-Well, you know! Kousei's\Ntotally helpless on his own, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only you'd be that honest\Nand tell him that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I wish he wouldn't go at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel anxious, and I get frustrated.\NI feel like being snarky to him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he said he wasn't going,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I felt relieved. And full of guilt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since I don't want him to see me like\Nthat, I'm doing my darnedest to put on an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have I always been so horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm discovering all these different sides\Nof myself that I never knew I had...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Facing all these different sides of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess that's also... What you call...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...being in love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is miles away.\NLet's call it a day. Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Um, Seto-sensei, I have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm counting on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.67,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital - 890m
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Arima-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to catch up to you\Njust walking at a normal pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You walk too slow. Your posture's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get a grip, or you'll look like a slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.69,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May your dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this Kimoto dude, he goes, "I'll play my\Noboe for you at the culture festival, Nagi-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How deluded is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that be pretty thrilling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depends on who.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.37,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Comes down to...                                              probably their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a realist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally got you to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-Not at all! Worry\Nabout you? Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be a bore to have a wuss\Nfor an enemy, that's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy, he's unbelievable, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's freaked out because he's got the\Nwhole score memorized perfectly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but he doesn't even bat an eyelash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he, a gunman out of a Western?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sounds like a die-cast robot\Nwith that heart of steel, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a hero, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I... supposed to tell him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck... Don't let him beat you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How irresponsible is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.55,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima\NSumitani Junior Highschool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Instead of thanking him, my selfish way of\Ncompensating for being so powerless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was only for self-satisfaction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an ugly phantom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kimoto-kun's gonna be a\Ngreat performer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important than you'd\Nthink, playing for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you going to play the\Npiano for? For someone else's sake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you started playing\Nthe piano for someone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's when you're able to play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you've shared those\Nsounds with tons of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you've reached tons of\Npeople with those sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when your hearts come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that music\Ntranscends words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a cliché. Women are realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We only believe in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.87,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May your dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ravel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to hear it!\NI don't want to hear it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to hear Ravel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Commit double suicide with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to hear it. I don't\Nwant to think about anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could just stop hearing everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.03,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way to visit my Kaori-chan\Nin the hospital. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to hold back because\Nof us. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you... don't you\Nthink you're being callous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After Kaori-chan did so much for\Nyou, why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't look good for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not true. It's not true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I made you remember something\Nyou don't want to remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess maybe we never\Nshould've met, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say a word.\NWhat could I have said to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How should I act when I see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my opinion, but... I think\Nyou should go see Kaori-chan after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if she was okay with me, I'd do\Nanything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it was for a girl I liked, I'd even drink muddy water,\Njust slurp-slurp-slurp, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what, I think for\NKaori-chan, I'm not the one, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she wants her own way\Nor needs to lean on somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she wants\Nsomebody to do something for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's you she always turns to, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enter a competition!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be my accompanist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could have a canelé.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please support me in this moment\Nthat I'm about to lose heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I just don't know what to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it... you'll know once you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A man can only take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not it's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the girl will let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I didn't think you'd ever come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I promised to bring you some canelés.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been practicing the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's everybody doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of answers are those?\NYou don't even want to be here, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but I don't know what to say, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just go back to the way things were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can just forget about it all, like\Nyou've pressed the reset button.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tap, tap, tap... like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that will make your heart lighter.\NThere's no point in remembering, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A violinist who can't hold\N her own bow... that's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would... why would\Nyou say such a thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all that howling, slapping me around,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}forcing me up onstage against my will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After carving so many scenes into\Nmy mind that I don't want to forget...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my canelé!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd let such a cranky whiner\Nhave it? I'd feel sorry for the canelé!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who asked for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're irresponsible!\NI wash my hands of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel so bitter... so bitter...\N And it's just so sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You gave me so many things...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't there anything I can do for you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it was for a girl I liked,\N I'd even drink muddy water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want him to notice... that\NI'm here... with my playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I drew this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat? You want to perform\Nat the culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A bolt out of the blue? I don't\Nget it! What are you thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! But it's your big moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do? Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only asked because\NI had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grovel some more, Kousei Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know where this is coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but since I was struggling to\Ncome up with a program...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I think it'll be intriguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-sensei... why do you want to\Nperform at the culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there, my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna discuss The Knight\Nof the Rose with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We reserved a booth at a diner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, let's have a crepe on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make it sound more springy.\NUse your wrists to play softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should wait an extra beat.\NSpeed up the intro and vary the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way! How many times did you go over it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's even more accurate than yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm not really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's pushing herself too hard, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mistake! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about misplaying the notes\Nsometimes. Let's hear you play it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck! We'll be there, no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're this year's main draw!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ibata-sensei will be in the audience.\NSo turn in a perfect performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he acknowledges your\Ntalent, you'll be set for life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear they're sending a reporter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're doing a feature on\N"a beautiful young female pianist."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Four more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Four more days. I only have four\Nmore days to make this piece my own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have high hopes for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She gets extra points for\Nher looks, don't you think?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The magazine writer's\Ncoming just to see Nagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll own everyone\Nelse without even trying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lolicon bait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your parents must be so proud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's nothing but a pretty face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to endure this\Nsuffering for another four days?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me, Mom... My hearing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, I'm a failure as an instructor.\NI'm about to let history repeat itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid. Even though\Nit's just a school event...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though it's not an\Nimportant competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all afraid. Even me, even Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure even Takeshi Aiza-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your whole life is condensed\Ninto a scant few minutes onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it's scary, and it\Nmakes no sense, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you still a pianist, Seto-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get past that, there's a\Nmoment when the slate gets wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the months of agony,\Nscreaming, suffering, and struggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a moment when\Nyou're rewarded for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you've reached tons\Nof people with those sounds,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when your hearts come together...\Nmusic just might transcend words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're creatures who just\N can't help ourselves... possessed by that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a little like being in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't monopolize the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, at least take the left leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your place is not here in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid to go out onstage\Nbecause you practiced so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave your body and soul to the piano,\Nand that's why you're afraid to expose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone calls you a "mentally unprepared\Ncoward," I'll kill them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throw out that non-existent chest of\Nyours. You're Kousei Arima's apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not! He's my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's settle this\Nonce and for all, onstage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't told you anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's you who's asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.11,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.74,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kuru School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the scent of pure, musical maidens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The place is packed\Nwith cute girls! Woo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a walking hard-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad they're plodding along like\Nthat when they've got those costumes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes them cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan will be up soon, right?\NHow did that turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? She wouldn't\Neven tell me a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she's outgrown\Nher big brother complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Must be sad for you, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did a good job!\N Huh? Where's Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Namahage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad kids will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're getting huge laughs?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's gonna make a serious act\Nlike ours stick out like a sore thumb!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This school festival is a terrifying event!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-O-Of course I'm\Nokay, why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite calm yourself, Arima-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lose your head more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so overwhelmed, I don't\Nhave time to be nervous, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. The first time I met you,\N your hand was trembling, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing,\Nyou pervert? You sexual harasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you squeeze my hand so\Nhard, your fingers will lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now open up your hand... and relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all afraid. Even me, even Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were you driven into a corner, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you afraid, too?\NThe same way... I am?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Just play with sincerity, give the performance\Nof your life with everything you've got."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... I've only lived for thirteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only been thirteen years... for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and for everyone who's watched you till now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's thirteen years that can't be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe in it, the time\Nyou've devoted to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Performer No. 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please take the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:43.76,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 18\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:55.07,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
